                "invention-title": [
                    "Efficient energy system of peak shaving power station and working method",
                    "一种调峰电站的高效能源系统及工作方法"
                ]
            },
            "abstract": [
                {
                    "p": "The invention relates to an efficient energy system of a peak shaving power station and a working method.The system comprises a power grid, an electrolytic cell, a solid hydrogen storage tank, an absorption heat pump and a fuel cell, the power grid is connected with the electrolytic cell, the electrolytic cell is connected with the solid hydrogen storage tank, and the absorption heat pump is connected with the solid hydrogen storage tank at the same time; the absorption heat pump is used for refrigerating by utilizing waste heat generated in the water electrolysis hydrogen production process of the electrolytic bath, and the produced cold energy is used for cooling the solid hydrogen storage tank; and the fuel cell is connected with the solid hydrogen storage tank. Waste heat in the hydrogen production and power generation process is fully utilized, the hydrogen storage density is increased through refrigeration, and the energy utilization rate of the energy storage power station is greatly increased. By the adoption of the technical scheme, the method has the advantages of being safe in technology, convenient, flexible, reliable, good in economical efficiency and the like; waste heat of the electrolytic cell and the fuel cell is fully utilized, and the energy utilization rate of the system can be effectively improved."
                },
                {
                    "p": "本发明涉及一种调峰电站的高效能源系统及工作方法，系统包括:电网、电解槽、固态储氢罐、吸收式热泵和燃料电池，电网与电解槽相连，电解槽与固态储氢罐相连，吸收式热泵同时与固态储氢罐相连，吸收式热泵利用电解槽电解水制氢过程中产生的余热，进行制冷，制取的冷量用于对固态储氢罐进行降温；燃料电池与固态储氢罐相连。本发明不仅充分利用了制氢和发电过程的余热，还通过制冷增大了储氢密度，大大提高了储能电站的能量利用率。本发明由于采取以上技术方案，具有技术安全、便捷、灵活、可靠、经济性好等优势；充分利用电解槽和燃料电池的余热，可有效提高系统的能量利用率。"
                }
            ]
